00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:13.670
In a major defeat for Donald Trump,

00:08:13.670 --> 00:08:16.040
a New York judge today ruled that the former president

00:08:16.040 --> 00:08:17.350
and his two eldest children--

00:08:17.350 --> 00:08:19.010
Ivanka and Donald Trump Jr-- must

00:08:19.010 --> 00:08:22.430
testify under oath in New York State civil investigation

00:08:22.430 --> 00:08:24.020
into his business practices.

00:08:24.020 --> 00:08:27.010
CBS's Catherine Herridge has more.

00:08:27.010 --> 00:08:29.650
The eight-page ruling from the New York judge

00:08:29.650 --> 00:08:31.540
means State Attorney General Letitia

00:08:31.540 --> 00:08:35.440
James can question former President Trump, Don Jr,

00:08:35.440 --> 00:08:37.780
and Ivanka about their business practices

00:08:37.780 --> 00:08:39.700
as part of a civil inquiry.

00:08:39.700 --> 00:08:42.310
And the court order sets a short timeline,

00:08:42.310 --> 00:08:46.270
ruling the Trumps must comply in full with existing subpoenas

00:08:46.270 --> 00:08:50.320
to provide records and sit for depositions within 21 days.

00:08:50.320 --> 00:08:52.540
I love loans.

00:08:52.540 --> 00:08:54.280
I love other people's money.

00:08:54.280 --> 00:08:58.180
Last month, James alleged the Trump organization repeatedly

00:08:58.180 --> 00:09:01.030
engaged in fraudulent and misleading practices

00:09:01.030 --> 00:09:04.540
to secure loans, tax benefits, and insurance coverage.

00:09:04.540 --> 00:09:06.370
The Trump organization is accused

00:09:06.370 --> 00:09:10.270
of inflating prices, including tripling the actual size of Mr.

00:09:10.270 --> 00:09:13.720
Trump's penthouse, which added about $200 million

00:09:13.720 --> 00:09:14.980
to the valuation.

00:09:14.980 --> 00:09:17.410
James also alleged the valuations

00:09:17.410 --> 00:09:19.990
of Trump golf courses in New York and Scotland

00:09:19.990 --> 00:09:21.550
were exaggerated.

00:09:21.550 --> 00:09:24.130
At today's contentious hearing, the Trump lawyers

00:09:24.130 --> 00:09:26.470
attacked James and her probe as tainted

00:09:26.470 --> 00:09:28.930
by political bias and an effort to pave

00:09:28.930 --> 00:09:31.570
the way for criminal charges in a separate case.

00:09:31.570 --> 00:09:34.510
The judge said their arguments missed the mark.

00:09:34.510 --> 00:09:36.820
Even if James dislikes Mr. Trump,

00:09:36.820 --> 00:09:39.790
it does not cross the line to unlawful discrimination

00:09:39.790 --> 00:09:43.310
and Mr. Trump has the right to plead the Fifth.

00:09:43.310 --> 00:09:44.270
And Catherine joins us.

00:09:44.270 --> 00:09:46.030
So how did Trump's lawyers respond?

00:09:46.030 --> 00:09:47.770
Well, Norah, even before the ruling,

00:09:47.770 --> 00:09:50.470
his lawyers indicated that they would appeal

00:09:50.470 --> 00:09:53.200
and that could delay or even de-sync

00:09:53.200 --> 00:09:54.530
the depositions all together.

00:09:54.530 --> 00:09:55.780
Catherine Herridge, thank you.

00:09:55.780 --> 00:09:56.620
You're welcome.

00:09:56.620 --> 00:09:58.210
Well, tonight, the police response

00:09:58.210 --> 00:10:00.010
to a fight at a New Jersey mall, has

00:10:00.010 --> 00:10:02.230
prompted an internal investigation

00:10:02.230 --> 00:10:05.350
after two officers handcuffed and pinned a Black teen

00:10:05.350 --> 00:10:07.960
to the floor while allowing another teen

00:10:07.960 --> 00:10:09.820
involved to sit on a couch.

00:10:09.820 --> 00:10:11.680
The Black teen's family is now demanding

00:10:11.680 --> 00:10:13.300
the officers be fired.

00:10:13.300 --> 00:10:14.530
Here's CBS's Jericka Duncan.

00:10:14.530 --> 00:10:17.060


00:10:17.060 --> 00:10:20.690
This video of two teens fighting inside a New Jersey mall

00:10:20.690 --> 00:10:22.160
has sparked outrage.

00:10:22.160 --> 00:10:24.530
Two officers intervened, one teen

00:10:24.530 --> 00:10:27.020
was allowed to sit on the sofa, the Black teen

00:10:27.020 --> 00:10:30.020
was placed in handcuffs with both officers kneeling

00:10:30.020 --> 00:10:31.490
on his back.

00:10:31.490 --> 00:10:32.570
It's because he's Black.

00:10:32.570 --> 00:10:35.540
What was your initial reaction to that video?

00:10:35.540 --> 00:10:39.140
Anger, hurt, disgust, disappointment.

00:10:39.140 --> 00:10:41.690
Ebony, who does not want to use her last name,

00:10:41.690 --> 00:10:44.570
says her 8th grade son's Z'Kye did not resist

00:10:44.570 --> 00:10:46.440
as officers handcuffed him.

00:10:46.440 --> 00:10:48.650
It made me feel like they're agreeing--

00:10:48.650 --> 00:10:52.280
and they were agreeing to him-- to me being inferior to him.

00:10:52.280 --> 00:10:56.060
Z'Kye who is 14 says he was trying to stop his 7th grade

00:10:56.060 --> 00:10:59.480
friend from being bullied by a 15-year-old named Joseph.

00:10:59.480 --> 00:11:02.390
I did not bully, tease them.

00:11:02.390 --> 00:11:05.600
We spoke to Joseph who says he's Hispanic.

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:09.170
I was confused why they were detaining him and not me.

00:11:09.170 --> 00:11:11.270
I even offered to get detained.

00:11:11.270 --> 00:11:14.280
When I was on the couch, I put my hands up like this,

00:11:14.280 --> 00:11:16.100
and I said, you guys could detain me.

00:11:16.100 --> 00:11:19.940
But she said no, because you were calm.

00:11:19.940 --> 00:11:22.620
Both officers are under investigation.

00:11:22.620 --> 00:11:25.160
Police did not charge the teens, still

00:11:25.160 --> 00:11:27.830
Ebony wants the officers to be held accountable

00:11:27.830 --> 00:11:29.750
and worries about her son.

00:11:29.750 --> 00:11:31.880
Have you ever had the conversation

00:11:31.880 --> 00:11:35.060
with your son about being a young man

00:11:35.060 --> 00:11:38.480
and being seen by some potentially as a threat?

00:11:38.480 --> 00:11:39.320
Absolutely.

00:11:39.320 --> 00:11:43.350
You have to have your Black man America talk to every boy.

00:11:43.350 --> 00:11:46.860
Jericka Duncan, CBS News, New York.

