00:16:24.010 --> 00:16:25.930
at America's military academies.

00:16:25.930 --> 00:16:28.330
And why the FDA is warning parents

00:16:28.330 --> 00:16:32.870
not to use some powdered baby formulas.

00:16:32.870 --> 00:16:35.270
Tonight's Eye on America segment is

00:16:35.270 --> 00:16:38.390
