00:16:40.130 --> 00:16:44.960


00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:46.380
Tonight, the Pentagon is reporting

00:16:46.380 --> 00:16:48.390
a record number of sexual assaults

00:16:48.390 --> 00:16:50.610
at US military service academies.

00:16:50.610 --> 00:16:54.990
131 assaults were reported during the 2020-21 school year.

00:16:54.990 --> 00:16:57.660
That's up 7% from 2019 when students

00:16:57.660 --> 00:16:59.460
were on campus all year.

00:16:59.460 --> 00:17:01.020
Officials say part of the reason may

00:17:01.020 --> 00:17:03.300
be that victims are more comfortable coming forward

00:17:03.300 --> 00:17:05.250
and reporting these incidents.

00:17:05.250 --> 00:17:07.800
All right, a safety warning tonight from the FDA

00:17:07.800 --> 00:17:10.170
for some powdered infant formulas.

00:17:10.170 --> 00:17:12.180
The agency is investigating complaints

00:17:12.180 --> 00:17:15.300
of at least four illnesses, including possibly one death,

00:17:15.300 --> 00:17:18.660
linked to formulas made at Abbott Nutrition at its plant

00:17:18.660 --> 00:17:20.400
in Sturgis, Michigan.

00:17:20.400 --> 00:17:22.860
The FDA is advising parents not to use

00:17:22.860 --> 00:17:26.250
certain batches of Similac, Alimentum or EleCare

00:17:26.250 --> 00:17:30.000
powdered infant formulas with an expiration date of April 1st

00:17:30.000 --> 00:17:31.030
or later.

00:17:31.030 --> 00:17:32.790
The company says it will do whatever it

00:17:32.790 --> 00:17:35.340
takes to resolve the situation.

00:17:35.340 --> 00:17:36.840
All right, coming up next.

