This is such a great story.

00:17:38.280 --> 00:17:42.120
An 11-year-old boy whose mullet won a contest but it

00:17:42.120 --> 00:17:47.150
is his heart that is getting all the attention.

00:17:47.150 --> 00:17:50.400
If you can't watch the CBS Evening News, you can listen.

00:17:50.400 --> 00:17:52.530
Subscribe wherever you get your podcasts.

