00:17:59.160 --> 00:18:02.220
Remote learning has resulted in some interesting fashion trends

00:18:02.220 --> 00:18:03.390
during the pandemic.

00:18:03.390 --> 00:18:05.910
Meet an Arkansas boy whose pandemic look is

00:18:05.910 --> 00:18:09.540
a cut above the rest, and it's all for a good cause.

00:18:09.540 --> 00:18:13.480
Here's CBS's Meg Oliver.

00:18:13.480 --> 00:18:17.410
During the pandemic, 12-year-old Allan Baltz found a new hairdo.

00:18:17.410 --> 00:18:19.360
Why did you choose a mullet?

00:18:19.360 --> 00:18:23.950
I'm like, what would really embarrass my sister the most?

00:18:23.950 --> 00:18:26.830
Leslie and Derek Baltz live in Jonesboro, Arkansas.

00:18:26.830 --> 00:18:28.690
Like parents across the country, they

00:18:28.690 --> 00:18:31.990
were desperate for creative ideas during 2020.

00:18:31.990 --> 00:18:35.680
Alice dyed her hair teal, I went red, Allan did a mullet.

00:18:35.680 --> 00:18:37.180
How did you feel about the mullet?

00:18:37.180 --> 00:18:41.410
At first, I was really questioning my parenting

00:18:41.410 --> 00:18:42.250
skills.

00:18:42.250 --> 00:18:45.070
But when a friend told them about the USA Mullet

00:18:45.070 --> 00:18:48.560
Championship, everything changed.

00:18:48.560 --> 00:18:51.320
I cannot believe this is a real thing.

00:18:51.320 --> 00:18:54.370
The Baltz is adopted Allan and Alice when they were five.

00:18:54.370 --> 00:18:56.470
Allan would only enter the contest

00:18:56.470 --> 00:19:00.830
if he could donate the $2,500 prize money to foster care.

00:19:00.830 --> 00:19:04.240
I was in foster care and I know completely how it feels

00:19:04.240 --> 00:19:07.360
and who would waste $2,500 or something?

00:19:07.360 --> 00:19:08.860
Not so important.

00:19:08.860 --> 00:19:12.220
The community rallied around him adding thousands more.

00:19:12.220 --> 00:19:14.860
I felt we had a chance to be near the top.

00:19:14.860 --> 00:19:18.160
But the kids sporting the cool shades and fresh suit

00:19:18.160 --> 00:19:22.330
won the illustrious title USA Mullet Champion.

00:19:22.330 --> 00:19:25.840
If you had one wish out of all of this, what would it be?

00:19:25.840 --> 00:19:28.060
No more kids being foster cared.

00:19:28.060 --> 00:19:33.030
Meg Oliver, CBS News, Jonesboro, Arkansas.

00:19:33.030 --> 00:19:34.920
I told you, he'd steal your heart.

00:19:34.920 --> 00:19:35.760
We'll be right back.

